Fujitsu RAID Server Template

Developed on Zabbix 3.4 for a Fujitsu Primergy RX350-S8. Contains basic Logical and Physical drive checks using the SNMPv2 agent.

Is it perfect? No. Is it complete? No. Is it free to use? Yes.

We couldn't find any alternative template, so we made it.

Damiano M., Gianluca R. Servizio informatica - Comune di Cervia
